    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designating the latter part of the last Quaternary glacial period, immediately preceding the current postglacial period, marked predominantly by the retreat of glaciers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
